<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11179</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18329</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西跺着小脚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18329</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21106</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁敢把火箭女孩儿变小！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21106</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小女孩儿现在看起来像个巨人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31530</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西看着小女孩儿蹦蹦跳跳走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31530</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36666</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啦啦啦啦啦！”小女孩儿唱着歌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36666</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43346</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西跟着小女孩儿飞，并用眼睛发射激光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43346</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49023</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嗞！小小的激光打中了小女孩儿的脖子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49023</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54091</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，都被弹开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54091</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西发射了一次又一次。嗞！嗞！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是什么？”小女孩儿摸着脖子说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“感觉有蚊子在叮我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77829</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小女孩儿蹦蹦跳跳又走了一会儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77829</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82899</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她抬头看到了美罗城大酒店。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82899</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87327</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这栋楼真可爱！”小女孩儿说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87327</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90688</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她用仪器瞄准大楼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90688</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94330</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我必须阻止这个小女孩儿。”罗西心想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94330</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97311</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但要怎么做呢？我太小了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97311</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西想了一会儿，有了主意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嗖！罗西飞进仪器里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在里面，她看到了各种电线和齿轮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116114</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西的眼睛再一次发射出激光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116114</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119888</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嗞！哐当！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119888</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123638</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小女孩儿手里的仪器爆炸了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123638</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125692</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西飞了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125692</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130099</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小女孩儿低头看着坏掉的仪器，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130099</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136314</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>吸了吸鼻子，嘴唇发抖，眼里含着泪水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136315</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142626</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！哇！”小女孩儿哭着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142626</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147755</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的收缩射线坏了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147755</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153692</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，一个男人和一个女人跑向小女孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153692</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157093</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们都穿着宇航服。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157093</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160242</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“艾巴！”男人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160242</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164113</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你妈妈和我一直在找你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164113</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170525</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“收缩射线坏掉了！”艾巴哭着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170525</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175118</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你不该玩儿那个！”小女孩儿的妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180053</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的爸爸看看四周，皱起了眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185706</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你为了你的收藏品，把很多东西都变小了吧？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185706</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187960</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾巴点点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187960</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191689</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你不应该那么做。”她妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191689</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起。”艾巴说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198756</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不让你外出了。”她爸爸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198756</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾巴的妈妈摸着下巴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202116</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我去把放大射线拿过来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205136</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209193</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西飞到艾巴妈妈面前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209193</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215184</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您好！”罗西说，“您能把‘人’重新变大吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215184</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218306</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然。”艾巴的妈妈说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218306</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223483</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所有的建筑和别的东西，我都会还原。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223483</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226454</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太好了！”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226454</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229350</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她想了一会儿又说：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229350</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234122</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，有一栋大楼可以不用还原。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239044</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>美罗城很快恢复了正常。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239044</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244327</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有的东西和人都恢复到正常大小。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244327</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250783</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾巴和她的父母回到了太空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256940</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西和朋友们走在回家的路上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256940</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262864</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看！”玛拉喊道，“旧电影院不见了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262864</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266162</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇。”杰克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266162</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271711</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许大家现在就可以建社区花园了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271711</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔用怀疑的眼神看着空地。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282019</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很想知道，火箭女孩儿跟这件事有没有关系。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285980</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西笑了。“谁知道呢？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285980</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295306</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这里有面包店。我们去买饼干吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>